USE \SISTEMAS\VENTAS\VENTASA\MIXTA ALIAS MIX
SET ORDER TO TAG GASCOD
COPY TO TMP
CLOSE DATA
USE TMP
REPL ALL TEXTO2 WITH STRTRAN(TEXTO2,".","")
